{{en-noun}}

# A [[thicket]], or an area [[overgrown]] with [[brier]]s etc. {{defdate|from 15th c.}}
#* {{quote-book|year=1807|author=William Wordsworth|title=Poems|section=Fidelity}}
#*: He halts, and searches with his eyes
